{"TopicId":205596,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How to make the Making History suits default?","CreatedByName":"1something","CreatedById":216937,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-13T00:55:40Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"1something","CreatedById":216937,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-13T00:55:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want the making history suit for all of my kerbals. Unfortunately, I am too lazy to got to every single one, click on the coat hanger and switch the suit. Is there a way to make the suit default or a shortcut to make all kerbals wear it or something?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbal Productions","CreatedById":208620,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-17T05:09:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224054456\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022205596\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221636764940\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216937\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00221something\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/13/2021 at 8:55 AM, 1something said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want the making history suit for all of my kerbals. Unfortunately, I am too lazy to got to every single one, click on the coat hanger and switch the suit. Is there a way to make the suit default or a shortcut to make all kerbals wear it or something?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m sorry, but\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Eas much as my knowledge on the game defaults says, there is no way. **\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027ll have to set it one-by-one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe default one is the white one for other kerbals and the orange is the default for the O4.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cb\u003E**This might be incorrect.\u003C/b\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-17T14:26:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe with mods?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbal Productions","CreatedById":208620,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-19T12:19:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224056205\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022205596\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221637159218\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210823\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AtomicTech\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/17/2021 at 10:26 PM, AtomicTech said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe with mods?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t think so.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BigFatStupidHead","CreatedById":44217,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-19T18:57:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d asked this question myself a while back for the Near Future suits, and the author of \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/185931-17-kerbal-occupation-colors-version-10\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EKerbal Occupation Colors\u003C/a\u003E made it an option for me. Now, it DOESN\u0027T work for assigning the Making History suits, but shows that it should be possible.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"1something","CreatedById":216937,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-20T23:53:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224056066\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022205596\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221637125746\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208620\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbal Productions\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/17/2021 at 4:09 PM, Kerbal Productions said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m sorry, but\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Eas much as my knowledge on the game defaults says, there is no way. **\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027ll have to set it one-by-one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe default one is the white one for other kerbals and the orange is the default for the O4.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cb\u003E**This might be incorrect.\u003C/b\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThats sad\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbal Productions","CreatedById":208620,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-21T01:20:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224057688\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022205596\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221637452418\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216937\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00221something\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, 1something said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThats sad\n\u003C/p\u00